"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-news-mathieu-van-der-poel-will-skip-mountain-bike-event-at-paris-olympics-to-focus-on-road-race\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"LIEGE, BELGIUM - APRIL 21: (L-R) Mathieu van der Poel of Alpecin - Deceuninck during the match between Liege v Bastogne - Liege 2024 - Men's Elite at the Liege on April 21, 2024 in Liege Belgium (Photo by Pim Waslander/Soccrates/Getty Images)  Soccrates Images/Getty Images  BRUSSELS - World champion Mathieu van der Poel will focus on the Olympic road race at the Paris Games this summer, after competing in the Tour de France, and skip mountain biking.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 181, \"end\": 186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\", \"score\": 0.9947890570658846, \"rank\": 0.0024069975612848837, \"text\": \"Liege\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Li\\u00e8ge\"}, {\"begin\": 187, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.9999961931764274, \"rank\": 3.758716402000211e-06, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mathieu van der Poel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mathieu van der Poel\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mathieu_van_der_Poel\"}, {\"begin\": 413, \"end\": 427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The versatile Dutch racer said that combining the Tour and the road race is \\\"the most logical\\\" choice.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.5517776819301846, \"rank\": 0.6494408507766284, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It ensures that I have a little more time and thus can prepare longer and better,\\\" he said in a statement released by his Alpecin-Deceuninck team.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel has won titles in many disciplines and thought at one point about competing in the cross-country mountain bike event at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But he faced what he called a \\\"difficult puzzle to put together\\\" with the route of the road race suiting his skills.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Just the road race?\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Only mountain biking?\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Or both?\\\"\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"he said.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whether or not in combination with the Tour de France, which I personally consider the best possible preparation for the Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel finally made his decision.\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Let us say I chose the most logical thing,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1261, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So, in consultation with the team, I opted for a slightly longer rest period, after which I can build up to the Tour de France and the Olympic road race without time pressure.\\\"\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1375, \"end\": 1389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 29-year-old rider, who has been in impressive form this year with victories at the Tour of Flanders and Paris-Roubaix classics, said he will work in support of teammate Jasper Philipsen \\\"in his hunt for stage wins and a possible green jersey\\\" of Tour de France's best sprinter.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1549, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}, {\"begin\": 1614, \"end\": 1630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasper_Philipsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jasper Philipsen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasper_Philipsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jasper_Philipsen\"}, {\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Points_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999480829168115, \"rank\": 5.191977877653686e-05, \"text\": \"green jersey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Points_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Points_classification_in_the_Tour_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1691, \"end\": 1705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And the goal is to win a stage myself this year,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Last year I got sick when there were a few stages where I had chances.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully I will be spared from that in this edition.\\\"\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel added that wearing the world champion's rainbow jersey this season played a role in his decision to race at the Tour.\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 2042, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1965, \"end\": 1979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"rainbow jersey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rainbow_jersey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a special year,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As world champion I like to ride in that jersey as much as possible.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So I also prefer not to miss the Tour de France.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2179, \"end\": 2193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that proved to be a good preparation last year, then towards the World Championships.\\\"\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also hinted that he could compete in mountain biking at future Olympics.\", \"from\": 2287, \"to\": 2362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel crashed out of the mountain bike race at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Who knows what's still possible in 2028 in Los Angeles?\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2482, \"end\": 2493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9986447774993905, \"rank\": 0.0013567307813245504, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's still a long time away, but I will be in a different phase of my career then,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Maybe then I can put everything on that mountain biking.\", \"from\": 2590, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This year the combination is just too difficult.\\\"\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2697, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Van der Poel, who is currently training in Spain, will not compete before the June 29-July 21 Tour de France.\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2742, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9885907772665178, \"rank\": 0.008072552667878317, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2793, \"end\": 2807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999999895783276, \"rank\": 6.0345056623022796e-09, \"text\": \"Tour de France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tour_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's Olympic road race is a challenging 170-mile (273-kilometer) trek set to take place on Aug. 3.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2940, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2914, \"end\": 2924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999101501129, \"rank\": 8.984988173537445e-08, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3118, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 3119, \"to\": 3167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\"